OL,3,C'Barricade the doors': Pupil describes
OL,4,Cschool lockdown terror as boy killed
OL,6,FA pupil who witnessed the aftermath of
OL,7,Fa fatal stabbing at a school in
OL,8,FSheffield has described how students
OL,9,Fwere told to "barricade" themselves in
OL,10,Fclassrooms as panic spread.
OL,12,FDivine Idahosa, 18, was at All Saints
OL,13,FCatholic High School when a 15-year-
OL,14,Fold boy was attacked on Monday
OL,15,Fafternoon.
