OL,3,C'Barricade the doors': Pupil describes
OL,4,Cschool lockdown terror as boy killed
OL,6,FSixth former Divine said: "I went
OL,7,Foutside and I saw three year 11s
OL,8,Fshouting, 'someone got stabbed, come
OL,9,Fhere' to a teacher. I didn't believe
OL,10,Fit at first so I went outside to see
OL,11,Fwhat was going on."
OL,13,FHe said he saw a body on the ground.
OL,14,FDespite a major emergency services
OL,15,Fresponse, the boy died at the scene.
