OL,3,C'Barricade the doors': Pupil describes
OL,4,Cschool lockdown terror as boy killed
OL,6,F"I was really really scared, I didn't
OL,7,Fbelieve it at first, but I saw what I
OL,8,Fsaw... the staff were scared - they
OL,9,Fdidn't know what to do but then they
OL,10,Fstarted saying 'go into classrooms,
OL,11,Flock the doors, shut the blinds,
OL,12,Fbarricade the doors' because they
OL,13,Fdidn't know if the person with the
OL,14,Fknife was on the loose or was trying
OL,15,Fto get other people as well."
OL,17,FDivine's brother, Leon, was at home
OL,18,Fwhen he was called by his brother.
