OL,3,C'Barricade the doors': Pupil describes
OL,4,Cschool lockdown terror as boy killed
OL,6,FHe said: "It doesn't feel real, it
OL,7,Ffeels like America - but this is
OL,8,FSheffield."
OL,10,FThe boys' mother, Patience, said she
OL,11,Frushed to the scene with Leon.
OL,13,FShe said: "We were saying to the
OL,14,Fpolice guys we were wanting to get in
OL,15,Fto get my son, because my son was on
OL,16,Fthe phone in a panic mode. But they
OL,17,Fsaid 'you can't go in'."
