OL,3,C'Barricade the doors': Pupil describes
OL,4,Cschool lockdown terror as boy killed
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder following the
OL,8,Fincident, which came just days after
OL,9,Fthe school reportedly implemented its
OL,10,Flockdown procedure following another
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FMrs Idahosa added: "Sheffield is
OL,14,Fbecoming something else. All Saints
OL,15,Fhas been a very good school, that's
OL,16,Fwhy people want to come here - they're
OL,17,Fdisciplined. But I don't know what's
OL,18,Fhappening now, I'm just terrified."
