OL,9,FI said 'again?' and she said 'yeah,
OL,10,Fthere's been a stabbing'. At the same
OL,11,Ftime my older daughter was calling...
OL,12,FI knew it was serious."
OL,14,FShe said she spoke to a friend and
OL,15,Fthey were "shaking and crying".
OL,17,F"They were under the tables," she
OL,18,Fsaid. "They did the same last week.
