OL,3,C'Barricade the doors': Pupil describes
OL,4,Cschool lockdown terror as boy killed
OL,6,F"You just feel unsafe. These are young
OL,7,Fkids coming to school to study but the
OL,8,Fenvironment they are in is now very
OL,9,Funreal."
OL,11,FSheffield Heeley MP Louise Haigh said
OL,12,Fthere were "serious questions... about
OL,13,Fhow this could have happened".
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police declined to
OL,16,Fanswer questions about whether the
OL,17,Farrested boy was known to the force,
OL,18,For comment on the reports of a
OL,19,Fprevious lockdown at the school.
